REFERENCE           KOWLOON_VOX_KOW1_S03_026A_CLAR
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CLARKE: ^7Avete respirato il gas?!?"

REFERENCE           KOWLOON_VOX_KOW1_S03_027A_HUDS
