REFERENCE           KOWLOON_VOX_KOW1_S07_116A_CLAR_M
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CLARKE: ^7Ah, giŕ... I numeri... sono la chiave per..."

REFERENCE           KOWLOON_VOX_KOW1_S07_117A_WEAV_M
